All models are configured with the same number of hidden units {64} and layers {3, 3, 2} for {R-GAT, R-GCN, S-HGN}, respectively. Additionally, the same HGNN models are implemented in SiHGNN, maintaining identical configurations for hidden units and layers as used on the GPUs.
